name: 日帰りGLOの男
description: Another early example of my glitch work, posted to Tumblr on October 15, 2014. This period is pre-watermark and before I incorporated animated subjects in my pieces, but the foundation of what would become the style I'm known for is all there. 455x680 pixels, 884.21 KB, 40 frames. Original 2014 post ---> https://n-lite.tumblr.com/post/100087629515/%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B0%E3%82%8Aglo%E3%81%AE%E7%94%B7
